            Full mechanical &amp; optical restoration
          </div>
          <div class="sx-badge">
            <svg class="sx-badge-icon" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1a7 7 0 1 0 0 14A7 7 0 0 0 8 1Zm3.1 5.37-3.5 3.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.7 0l-1.5-1.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .7-.7L7.25 8.8l3.15-3.13a.5.5 0 1 1 .7.7Z"/></svg>
            Shoots SX-70 &amp; 600 film
          </div>
          <div class="sx-badge">
            <svg class="sx-badge-icon" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1a7 7 0 1 0 0 14A7 7 0 0 0 8 1Zm3.1 5.37-3.5 3.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.7 0l-1.5-1.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .7-.7L7.25 8.8l3.15-3.13a.5.5 0 1 1 .7.7Z"/></svg>
