  {%- comment -%} ── Under-fold spec strip ──
      Mini-specs (Film / Board / Condition) + the longer "Every SX-70 we
      restore..." summary line. Was previously inside the right-column
      info pane; moved out here so the title + description sit higher and
      this restoration summary anchors the transition into the green
      OpenSX70 chapter directly below. {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="sx-summary-strip">
    <div class="sx-summary-strip-inner">

      {%- comment -%} ── Sample frames row ──
          Three sample images shot with this camera (or representative
          SX-70 frames). Configured via section settings so each PDP can
          have its own set, falling back to placeholders if not set.
          The "01 / 02 / 03" eyebrows on each frame suggest "test roll"
          / film-strip ordering and give the row a documentary feel. {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="sx-summary-photos">
        {%- assign photo_1 = section.settings.sample_photo_1 -%}
