              <tr>
                <td>Flash Metering</td>
                <td>Basic flashbar support. Limited models meter flash properly.</td>
                <td>Real-time flash metering on all models. Reads reflected light for correct exposure.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Low Light Warning</td>
                <td>None. You find out when you get a dark print.</td>
                <td>Solid red LED when light is too low for handheld.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Ejection Control</td>
                <td>Immediate ejection. No way to shield print.</td>
                <td>Hold shutter to delay ejection. Protect print from bright light.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Manual Control</td>
                <td>None. Fully automatic only.</td>
                <td>With dongle: 1/2000 &ndash; 1s, B and T modes, strobe sync, multi-exposure, self-timer.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>External Flash</td>
