        <div class="sx-dgrid-card">
          <span class="sx-dgrid-num">04</span>
          <div class="sx-dgrid-body">
            <div class="sx-dgrid-name">Self Timer</div>
            <div class="sx-dgrid-desc">10-second LED countdown, then the camera closes the shutter and flips the mirror before firing — reducing shake for sharper images. Sonar cameras get autofocus too.</div>
